text: Annelies Dom (born 8 April 1986) is a Belgian professional racing cyclist, who currently rides for UCI Women's Continental Team . Dom will retire at the end of the 2020 season, after eight years as a professional cyclist. ==Major results== ;2013 : 3rd Time trial, National Road Championships ;2018 : 1st 20px Road race, National Road Championships : 1st 20px Points race, National Track Championships ==See also== * List of 2015 UCI Women's Teams and riders ==References== ==External links== * * Category:1986 births Category:Living people Category:Belgian female cyclists Category:Place of birth missing (living people)
